'''Chaos troopers''' served the [[Krath/Legends|Krath]] during the time of the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]].

During the rise of the Krath cult, many followers were brainwashed by the teachings of [[Satal Keto/Legends|Satal Keto]] to become willing [[Death/Legends|suicide]] warriors who would [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] the [[CX-133 Chaos fighter|Chaos Fighter]] into enemy [[Starship/Legends|ships]]. They served as living [[Missile/Legends|missiles]] and this they did gladly.

